0479			;THE DATA DISPLAY FROM THE DISPLAY TABLE.  
0479			;THE MENU ENTRY NUMBER FROM THE MENU DRIVER HAS AN EQUIVALENT HERE. IT IS THE ACTIVE WINDOW  
0479			;NUMBER AND IS USEDIN IDENTICAL FASHION.  
